  [2]: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/xamarin/xamarin-forms/app-fundamentals/app-lifecycle#page-notification-events
  [3]: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/xamarin/xamarin-forms/app-fundamentals/messaging-center

